    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Two-dimensional figures that can be dressed in corresponding garments, intended for children's play. These are most often made of paper or cardboard, but may be made of other materials, such as vinyl. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
